1. ADDING A NEW PRODUCT IN FOREMAN
================================================================

Step 1:  Log in to the Foreman/Katello web UI.

Step 2:  Navigate to:
         Content --> Products

Step 3:  Click "New Product" (top-right button).

Step 4:  Fill in the details:
         - Name        : e.g., Ubuntu_24.04
         - Label       : Auto-filled (or set manually)
         - GPG Key     : (optional, add if you have one)
         - Description : (optional)

Step 5:  Click "Save".

The product is now created and ready for repositories to be added.


