3. SYNCING REPOSITORIES
================================================================

Step 1:  Go to Content --> Products --> [Your Product Name]

Step 2:  Click the "Repositories" tab.

Step 3:  Select the checkboxes next to the repos you want to sync
         (or select all).

Step 4:  Click "Sync Now".

Step 5:  Monitor sync progress:
         Content --> Sync Status
         - Green "Success" = sync completed OK
         - Red "Failed"    = check URL or network connectivity

Optional: Schedule recurring syncs via:
         Content --> Sync Plans --> New Sync Plan
         Then assign the plan to your product.

Verify repo content after sync:
         Content --> Products --> [Product] --> Repositories
         --> Click repo name --> "Packages" tab


